thread.title: Carina M.

author: Carina M.
title: Carina M.
text:
I've to thanks the customer assistance for their help! Without them, I would buy lenses that would make my glasses unusable for me.
The eyeglasses are super! I love them! I have a very strong prescription, and I was a little scared that the lenses wouldn't do the job, but they work perfectly! Great product for the price.
The shipping was super fast.
I will definitely buy more!
